specialtyItem.attributes_description: Increases ATK and Crit. DMG of all Resonators in the team by 10% and 16% respectively, lasting for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
specialtyItem.bg_description:
Snacks kept by Youhu in her ice cauldron, always cool to the touch. 
It’s difficult for Youhu to find food and accommodations while she travels around Solaris hunting for antiquities. These tasty cakes are what keep her from starving at times like these.
Youhu likes to put fruits in the cauldron too. As a result, the moist crusts of the cakes always gives off the faint fragrance of the seasonal fruits.

resultItem.name: Pizza Classica
resultItem.attributes_description: Increases Basic Attack DMG Bonus of all Resonators in the team by 40% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description:
A traditional dish from Rinascita, topped with gemberry jam, cheese, and smoked sausage. When it comes out of the oven, it fills the air with a rich aroma.
There was a man who swore he'd never have olives on his pizza, but the more he resisted, the more olives he got.

specialtyItem.name: A Slice of Pizza
specialtyItem.attributes_description: Increases Basic Attack DMG Bonus of all Resonators in the team by 44% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
specialtyItem.bg_description:
A slice cut from an unimaginably large pizza, rich with melted cheese and laden with various toppings. Every child can find a slice they like, making for a rare treat eaten together only once a month.

The nannies used to say, "Love inspires faith, faith fosters sharing, and sharing brings love full circle."

resultItem.name: Pizza Tropicale
resultItem.attributes_description: Increases Healing Bonus of all Resonators in the team by 25% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description:
A non-traditional dish from Rinascita, topped with gemberry jam, cheese, and crownapple. When it comes out of the oven, it elicits gasps and cries.
1. NEVER mention Pizza Tropicale to a Ragunnesi.
2. NEVER mention crownapple to a Ragunnesi.
3. NEVER mention apple or crown...

resultItem.name: Triple-Scoop Ice Cream
resultItem.attributes_description: Reduces Flight STA consumption for all Resonators in the team by 15% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description: Three perfectly stacked scoops of ice cream, balanced on a crunchy cone. Each scoop brings a different flavor, and every bite tastes like joy.

specialtyItem.name: Multi-Scoop Ice Cream
specialtyItem.attributes_description: Reduces Flight STA consumption for all Resonators in the team by 18% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
specialtyItem.bg_description: With a makeshift mini ice cream maker, Roccia serves up simple ice cream that's both generous in portion and light on the pocket. It's become a beloved treat among the troupe, satisfying their cravings for sweets without straining their budget.

resultItem.name: Nuvola Pasta
resultItem.attributes_description: Reduces Wall Dash and Swimming STA consumption for all Resonators in the team by 30% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description: Pasta made with Mastic Nuvola, known for its strong, inviting fragrance. It is said that the fragrance attracts the singing wraiths from the Nimbus Sanctum. People often venture out at dawn to gather fresh Mastic Nuvola, hoping to catch the melody it holds within.

specialtyItem.name: One-Pot Pasta
specialtyItem.attributes_description: Reduces Wall Dash and Swimming STA cost for all Resonators in the team by 35% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
specialtyItem.bg_description:
Zani's pasta is a rich and flavorful dish, made by layering hearty meat sauce with cheese, sausage, and fragrant herbs before cooking it to perfection.
According to what she said, she first stumbled upon the idea while reheating a takeout meal that had gone cold after a long workday. On a whim, she threw in whatever ingredients she had on hand, and to her surprise, the result was unexpectedly delicious. What began as a quick fix soon turned into a carefully refined recipe.

resultItem.name: Ragunna Espresso
resultItem.attributes_description: Reduces Flight STA consumption for all Resonators in the team by 10% for 15m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description:
A traditional coffee from Ragunna, rich and intense. Finishing a cup of Ragunna Espresso without flinching is a true mark of adulthood.
"You've already had three cups today!"
"But this is only my third task!"

specialtyItem.name: Orange Espresso
specialtyItem.attributes_description: Reduces Flight STA consumption for all Resonators in the team by 12% for 15m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
specialtyItem.bg_description: An espresso with a hint of orange, this has become Carlotta's morning ritual since joining the Montelli family. The bold coffee flavor is mellowed by a citrusy sweetness, creating a refreshing balance. It's perfect for those gearing up for a challenge or unwinding after one.

resultItem.name: Steak Margherita
resultItem.attributes_description: Increases Resonance Liberation DMG Bonus of all Resonators in the team by 40% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description: A massive, freshly cooked steak perfect for a family gathering. According to a well-meaning local, the only proper way to enjoy Steak Margherita is medium-rare. Noted. But let's go with medium-well, just to be safe.

resultItem.name: Laurus Salad
resultItem.attributes_description: Increases Healing Bonus of all Resonators in the team by 30% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description:
Freshly mixed with Viscum Berries and Laurus Sprouts, this salad is light, sweet, and healthy.
Acolytes of the Order regard the Viscum Berry as the "holy nourishment of the wise." They chew the fruit alongside sacred texts, believing that doing so imprints the teachings upon the soul.

specialtyItem.name: Knight-Errant's Essentials
specialtyItem.attributes_description: Grants 34% Healing Bonus to all Resonators in the team for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
specialtyItem.bg_description:
Prepared by Cartethyia herself, this Laurus Salad comes packed with extra Viscum Berries, crispy and sweet.
Now a wandering knight, she's hungry to learn, to grow, and to see the world.
Let's start with a salad made just for the wandering knight. This time, extra berries included!

resultItem.name: Nectarwine
resultItem.attributes_description: Increases Healing Bonus of all Resonators in the team by 15% for 15m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description: Brewed from the nectar of Sunflare Everlasting, this mead is gifted by the Montelli family to each of its new members. To drink this mead is to let go of old grudges, and show the truest of hearts.

resultItem.name: Daily Panini
resultItem.attributes_description: Increases Energy Regen of all Resonators in the team by 25% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description:
The perfect morning sandwich—delicious, quick, and wholesome. 
Even the simplest bread holds infinite potential. Like life, a panini may seem the same every day, but it is always a little different.

specialtyItem.name: Homemade Panini
specialtyItem.attributes_description: Increases Energy Regen of all Resonators in the team by 28% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
specialtyItem.bg_description:
A Panini made by Cantarella herself.

Two pieces of perfectly baked, crispy bread are stuffed with a blend of carefully seasoned seafood.

With each bite, the rich flavors slide down your throat and settle in your stomach, filling it with unparalleled satisfaction.

Unlike potions' mysterious flavors, this is a taste of simple comfort and warmth.

resultItem.name: Every Flavor Bell Crab
resultItem.attributes_description: Increases ATK and Crit. Rate of all Resonators in the team by 22% and 12% respectively for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description: The troupe's favorite seafood, Bell Crab, is the soul of this dish. Each Bell Crab finds its perfect shell, giving it a distinct flavor. Before every meal, the troupe members place a bet: What will the next crab taste like?

resultItem.name: Baton Bread
resultItem.attributes_description: Increases Healing Bonus and Max HP of all Resonators in the team by 5% and 10% respectively for 15m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description: A bread that looks like a baton and tastes like one. Rumor has it, someone once tried to use it as the main shaft for an aircraft—fortunately, that idea never took off.

specialtyItem.name: Pasta Bocadillo
specialtyItem.attributes_description: Gives 8% Healing Bonus to all Resonators in the team and increases their Max HP by 12% for 15m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
specialtyItem.bg_description:
For a wandering bard like Ciaccona, meals on the road are all about striking a balance between taste and convenience.
One day, as the campfire crackled to life, she had an idea and took the bread she always carried.
As the rich aroma of meat sauce filled the air, seeping into the bread's warm crust, she spread on the final layer of seasoning.
However, there's an unspoken rule. Ragunna's pasta is not to be tampered with. No shortcuts, no twists. Taking a bite of her creation, Ciaccona was lost in her thoughts. "If I ever get banished, this bread might just be one of the reasons."

resultItem.name: Troupe Strength
resultItem.attributes_description: Increases Heavy Attack DMG Bonus of all Resonators in the team by 25% for 15m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description: The troupe's self-brewed liquor, its name a symbol of ownership, power, and honor. The seafarers used to bicker endlessly over what to call it. After many wagers and a fair bit of their private stock on the line, the drunken Fools finally reached a decision: it would be called "Troupe's Strength."

specialtyItem.name: Purity Strength
specialtyItem.attributes_description: Increases Heavy Attack DMG Bonus of all Resonators in the team by 28% for 15m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
specialtyItem.bg_description:
Crafted by Brant himself, this exceptional brew offers a refreshing flavor with a lingering aftertaste.

Just as he dedicates his soul to every performance on stage, Brant pours his passion into each bottle.

With his name signed proudly on the bottle, he extends his heartfelt well wishes to those who receive this meticulously prepared gift.

"Life is to celebrate and to embrace freedom."

resultItem.name: Gold Star Pizza
resultItem.attributes_description: Increases Resonance Skill DMG Bonus of all Resonators in the team by 50% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description: Now available at Trattoria Margherita in Ragunna City, a new pizza said to come from the distant land of Huanglong. With a unique topping of beef, pineapple, durian, and cheese, this pizza delivers a flavor that surprises and lingers. As fans of this bold combo always say, "It hits like a wave!"

resultItem.name: Every Flavor Bell-less Crab
resultItem.attributes_description: Increases all team members' ATK by 22% and Crit. DMG by 24% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description: Bell Crabs shed their iconic bells during certain times of the year. During this period, these crabs are also known as "Bell-less Crabs," said to have a distinct flavor apart from Bell Crabs.

resultItem.name: Wine-Brewed Octopus Clam
resultItem.attributes_description: Increases all team members' Max HP by 30% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description: It is said that a drunken Troupe member once mistook wine for water while cooking seafood, accidentally creating this dish. Fortunately, no fires were involved.

resultItem.name: Riccioli Salt Baked Fish
resultItem.attributes_description: Increases all team members' DEF by 35% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description: The finest ingredients often require only the simplest preparation. Fresh fish, lightly cleaned and baked in sea salt, brings out its pure, natural flavors. For seasoned sailors, this dish is a commonplace staple. However, for the sheltered nobles of Ragunna, it represents their most vivid imagination of the sea.

resultItem.name: Oaknut Honeycake
resultItem.attributes_description: Reduces Flight STA consumption for all Resonators in the team by 10% for 15m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description:
Add more syrup! No, even more! Until this honeycake is as sweet and warm as a hug! And don't forget to top it with some Oaknuts, the forest's blessings and nature's gift.
May you have a sweet day.

specialtyItem.name: Redcurrant Tart
specialtyItem.attributes_description: Reduces Flight STA consumption for all Resonators in the team by 12% for 15m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
specialtyItem.bg_description: A tart drenched in thick, tangy jam that floods every crevice of the pastry, overpowering its sweetness. No one but Phrolova enjoys this zesty flavor, nor does anyone know where the tiny, sour berries even come from.

resultItem.name: Saltimbocca
resultItem.attributes_description: Grants 40% Resonance Liberation DMG Bonus to all Resonators in the team for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description:
A traditional Septimont dish made from mashed veal and Bloodleaf Viburnums.
It's said that it leaps into your mouth and gives you courage for battle.
Septimontians drum and feast before the hunt. They defend their home with blood and flesh.

resultItem.name: Glory Roast Platter
resultItem.attributes_description: Grants 50% Healing Bonus to all Resonators in the team for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description:
Skewers, poultry legs, and meat wraps. Now you've got yourself a Glory Roast Platter!
Come, Hero of Gladiators, Star of the Arena, take this "glory" and let's meet at the top!

resultItem.name: Frosted Cream Blizzard
resultItem.attributes_description: Grants 25% Healing Bonus to all Resonators in the team for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description:
A cup of seemingly ordinary shaved ice. Is it really as ordinary as it looks?
...Alright, yes. It is absolutely ordinary. But for Septimontians, this simple treat is one of the few chances to truly cool down.

resultItem.name: Solis
resultItem.attributes_description: Increases Energy Regen of all Resonators in the team by 30% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description:
A popular energy drink among Septimont Gladiators.
Drink this can of Solis, and fight 'til the last breath!

specialtyItem.name: Heartpour
specialtyItem.attributes_description: Increases Energy Regen of all Resonators in the team by 34% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
specialtyItem.bg_description:
Endorsed by Gladiator Star Lupa, it's still a hit across Septimont.
Lightly sweet, refreshingly smooth, and coming in a variety of flavors, it is best enjoyed ice cold.
For Lupa, fighting in the arena is an indispensable part of her life. At the breaks of matches, she still takes a sip of this Heartpour, remembering the thrill of the fight and the laughter she shared with her partner during the Agon of Champions.

resultItem.name: Bamboo Iris Crisps
resultItem.attributes_description: Increases ATK of all Resonators in the team by 25% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description:
A local Septimontian Snack made from fried petals of Bamboo Iris. Light and crunchy.
Each pack holds just a few Bamboo Iris Crisps... and a whole lot of deliciously fragrant air. You won't stop at just one.

resultItem.name: Seasalt Popcorn
resultItem.attributes_description: Grants 10% Healing Bonus to all Resonators in the team and increases their Max HP by 20%, lasting for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description: Seasalt Popcorn, your must-have snack for any Agon. Salty, joyful, and healthy! Every bite brings the taste of the sea.

resultItem.name: Bubbly Buddy
resultItem.attributes_description: Grants 30% Heavy Attack DMG Bonus to all Resonators in the team for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
resultItem.bg_description:
Whether you're watching Agons or catching every clash in the arena, it's there for you.
Zero sugar. Zero calories. Packed with Bloodleaf Viburnums. Let it fire up the arena!
